{"tid":1416184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好搞罷工太密！民航署可能係救香港唯一出路","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:43:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T12:03:38.000Z","uid":113516,"like":322,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"6b75ba7282ee4bb53c02e582671e8e31bdbac49b","tid":1416184,"uid":113516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:43:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>轉貼</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n民航署一手料：政府要冷處理機場罷工<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民航署可能係救香港唯一出路</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n傳說我個朋友屋企人做民航署<br />\n<br />\n早於一個月前，話政府已經冷處理所有關於機場同民航署嘅新聞<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>請留意，機場集會無阻止無警察<br />\n<br />\n今日航空控制員罷工<br />\n<br />\n機場取消咁多班機<br />\n<br />\n林鄭政府隻字不提，只提狗鐵</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解？因為唔想人諗起機場，諗起民航署 (冷處理）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>航空控制員係無可取代嘅職業<br />\n<br />\n唔似紮鐵，工作要經過好多training<br />\n<br />\n絕對唔可以即刻搵人替工</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢地亦受國際航空法保障<br />\n<br />\n隨時按章罷工<br />\n<br />\n合情合理合法<br />\n<br />\n不能炒，不能扣人工<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">飛行令1995<br />\n<br />\n「禁止航空交通管制員在感到疲倦，或受對精神有影響的物品影響的情況下行使執照特權」</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只要佢地長期罷工，機場根本癱瘓</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">林鄭今朝記者會唔敢講，就係最驚依班公務員</span><br />\n<br />\n當然全個機場員工罷工病假，成件事就更加有影響力<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>求push 求推post，你地聽日唔好再搞罷工<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n利申: 唔係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好話我係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我剩係想大家唔好搞罷工太密，香港仲有好多未開發既市民，政府依家係打民意戰，政府日日搞記招，俾市民睇示威者點搞到交通死哂，就係想拉攏呢堆藍絲中游市民要支持政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae5d291e20ca3d7b6ad35fb22c25720b79a1b99","tid":1416184,"uid":113516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:43:44.000Z","msg":"[係有d道理] 機場迎接親友活動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385896\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385896</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8be515e31e7c9182e98ef756d55d35251747a55e","tid":1416184,"uid":113516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:43:56.000Z","msg":"[係有d道理] 機場迎接親友活動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385896\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385896</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d36efb573ea993d23a4cbad01ad1bb9e7ae01b","tid":1416184,"uid":141148,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:44:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"354fb6b9e5204254808b20edc8e6653c12e78843","tid":1416184,"uid":113516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:44:28.000Z","msg":"[係有d道理] 機場迎接親友活動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385896\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385896</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b729fc91c758